           <p>After just 7 weeks into the Web Development bootcamp of Le Wagon, me and my teammates, Vincent Bohec and Zlatko Naumoski, made a fun Airbnb clone website that, instead of renting apartments, rents out books!</p>
           <p>Our biggest challenge was finishing the whole idea in 1 week. Like a new born deer, wobbly on our legs, we tackled building the app in a record time. Having never worked on a web project like this with teammembers before, it was a gigantic learning experience for all of us.</p>
         </div>
         <div>
           <p>We figured out how to divide our responsibilities by working in silos and always reminding ourselves of the MVC pattern. This project has been the backbone of teaching me project implementation and teamwork and I would have not been this confident in my web dev skills if it wasn't for this project.</p>
